T02TD2326E:267b-1: pradzny'a p'a ra mi t'a s'a dh'a nam /
T02TD2326E:267b-3: shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa'i sgrub thabs /
T02TD2326E:267b-4: 'jam dpal smra ba'i seng ge la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD2326E:267b-5: yum gyi sgrub pa bshad par bya //
T02TD2326E:267b-6: shes rab pha rol phyin 'byung ba'i //
T02TD2326E:267b-7: gang zhig bsgoms btsam gyis ni //
T02TD2326E:267b-8: rgol ba thams cad tshar gcod pa //
T02TD2326E:267b-9: zhal gcig phyag ni gnyis pa ste //
T02TD2326E:267b-10: sku mdog dkar zhing yid 'ong ma //
T02TD2326E:267b-11: skra bcings pa la cung zhig 'phyang //
T02TD2326E:267b-12: chu skyes dkar la legs gnas pa //
T02TD2326E:267b-13: phyag g-yas su ni padma ste //
T02TD2326E:267b-14: kha dog dmar ba'i rnam par bsgom //
T02TD2326E:267b-15: shes rab pha rol phyin pa g-yon //
T02TD2326E:267b-16: rdo rje skyil krung legs par bcas //
T02TD2326E:267b-17: rgyan kun gyis ni legs par brgyan //
T02TD2326E:267b-18: lte ba'i dkyil 'khor dag tu bsgom //
T02TD2326E:267b-19: aa yig yi ge la zhugs shing //
T02TD2326E:267b-20: mchog tu dga' bar byed pa'o //
T02TD2326E:267b-21: dam tshig sems dpa' rnam bskyed la //
T02TD2326E:267b-22: ye shes sems dpa' rnam par bsgom //
T02TD2326E:267b-23: zla ba drug gi sbyor ba yis //
T02TD2326E:267b-24: shes rab pha rol phyin par 'gyur //
T02TD2326E:267b-25: mtshan ma bdun gyi sbyor ba yis //
T02TD2326E:267b-26: bstan bcos kun la mkhas par 'gyur //
T02TD2326E:267b-27: zla ba shar ba'i rim gyis ni //
T02TD2326E:267b-28: zla ba phyed ni bsgom par bya //
T02TD2326E:267b-29: bzlas pa 'bum byas sbyor ba yis //
T02TD2326E:267b-30: nyin re bzhin du tshigs bcad brgya //
T02TD2326E:267b-33: de la sngags ni 'di yin te //
T02TD2326E:267b-34: aom pi tsu pi tsu pradzny'a bardha ni /
T02TD2326E:267b-35: dzva la dzva la me dha bardha ni //
T02TD2326E:267b-36: dhi ri dhi ri budhi bardha ni sv'a h'a /
T02TD2326E:267b-37: bya rog gi skad ma grag par sngags 'di lan bdun du mngon par bsngags par byas nas /
T02TD2326E:268a-0: ma brlang pa'i skyur po'i khu ba 'thungs na zla ba drug tu @268a * //
T02TD2326E:268a-2: de shes rab chen po dang ldan par 'gyur ro //
T02TD2326E:268a-3: shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa'i sgrub thabs //
T02TD2326E:268a-4: rje btsun ka ma la sh'i las mdzad pa rdzogs so//
